Switch pMode
	Case kSpllRsltAutoChangeWord,kSpllRsltCondChangeWord,kSpllRsltMisspelledWord
		Calculate ivPrompt as kStrNotInDictionary
	Case kSpllRsltDoubledWord
		Calculate ivPrompt as kStrDuplicateWord
	Case kSpllRsltMixedDigitsWord
		Calculate ivPrompt as kStrMixedDigits
	Case kSpllRsltUncappedWord
		Calculate ivPrompt as kStrUncapped
End Switch
Redraw {Prompt}